column5: Lookin pretty snazzy Terry........very nice !!!!
Now theres a word ya dont hear everyday anymore.  Lew you put a smile on me face with that.
Smiles are what I do best, my friend
Great price an a fine looking boat, she should serve you well.
Nice ride and great price for sure! Good luck on your fishin trip Terry!

Terry you did well .Sylvan makes a fine boat.Now get out there and enjoy fishing in comfort.Maybe I should hitch a ride with you this fall at Quinte .Looks alot warmer than an open tiller.By the way when is the gang all heading up this year?I dont want to wish the rest of the summer away but I cant wait for those fall quinte walleye and the OFC get together.Congrats on the ride shes a beaut!Dan
Nice boat and a great price! Is that trailer big enough? It looks alittle small for that boat...
Good stuff Terry, Great deal, enjoy!  Maureen
Nice looking ride Terry!  Congrats!  Now about that day on the water you owe me........
yeah I think the trailer could be a bit wider  and I owe a few people a day on the water...where and when do you want to go
I have always wanted to TARPON fish.
I can't go but  I will lend you the boat for that one  let me know how you do
I'll go with you Brian since Terry can't make it.  Terry - when you get back from your trip we'll set something up.  Have a great time!
Nice ride Terry. That's a similar model to my Lund. You'll love it I'm sure. Now let's see some fish pictures taken inside the boat!!!
We got a week to get r done bud.  Terry,where are the keys? Ah that is the question.

well as the subject states I have bought another boat after selling my  nitro boat  1998 SYLVAN PRO SELECT 1600 with a 90 hp on it      well I pick it up tomorrow and get to park it cause I am off to shiningtree for a week on my yearly trip....so it will be a couple of weeks till I can take her for a spin anyways it should serve me well for the type of fishing I do these days  can't wait to play....here fishy fishy fishy
nice new to you ride.congrats and hope you have nothing but enjoyment with it
Nice ride Terry! Lookin forward to seeing it out on Quinte this fall... looks like the perfect boat for those waters and Simcoe! Enjoy! HH
Should be a nice ride. BTW, if you don't mind, what did it run you? I'm thinking about picking up a boat in the next year or two and I have to start planning (greasing the wife). Thanx.
WTG Terry. A perfect boat for you. I just can't see you on Quinte doing pickerel in the fall with a bass boat. You'll be much more comfortable. Congrats.
YEE HAA. Full windshield and a cover. See you on Quinte in December.
Congrats!  Great looking boat!  I'm getting jealous seeing everyone's boats on here...gonna have to get one myself...in about 10 years....LOL.
she cost me $8000.00  yeah  Quinte and me should meet a few times this fall
Very nice boat Terry.  That's a good price too  Sweet!!  Joey
Nice Ride Terry!  Congrats
If ya need any "ballast" on Quinte this fall Terry... just drop me a line! HH
Congrats Terry, looks like a nice ride... I think you got a nice deal on it too! -Brian
You go ahead and prance around in your sweet boat while the rest of us stand at shore and drool! hahahaha  After I win Super 7 tomorrow I will post a pic of my new boat... I mean Yacht

Well my friend,you and I, have had some great discussion about selling yer Nitro and what to buy if you did. Ya got me hooked in this bass fish,n thing,bought meself a bass boat and ya went on and sold yers. I gots to say,I got nothing but good things to say about that new vessel of yers. I can see us out there,late May early June, down rigg,n for some lakers and whites on yers,and pitch,n and flipp,n and dragg,n tubes from mine. Maybe the thought of selling mine just got put on the back burner.Hell,ya gots yerself a great boat there. Congrats.    BTW,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Do you need a front pedistal seat made for it. F L M A O.  Nice boat bud. Good on ya.
I just noticed the MINI windshied in the front,whats that all about. L M A O.
Beautiful rig Terry, love the all weather canopy.  Cheers, 1leg
thanks all  that extra windshield is on the boat next to it  but you had me looking for a minute.....LOL there is a small trolling motor on the front too  might have to beef it up a bit
Wow Terry... WTG.. Nice looking ride  Congrats...
thanks we will all be out there fishing for whitefish and trout
I got a buyer for that when u upgrade.  Pops looking for one.

I will keep that in mind it will be 2 weeks before I get to try any of it......but I will be fishing  about 12 hours a day all next week..in a 14ft with an 8 hp yamaha ..and my found back  lakes on the ATV........can't wait....
Why dont I take a day off next week and SLIME IT for ya.
Good Luck with the boat and on your trip. It should do you well, as a great all purpose fishing machine.  Congrats on the purchase.
If it suits your needs it is your perfect boat.

Awsome ride Terry that is what I am also waiting to get they are a nice boat you should have alot of great trips in her BTW if you need to make her feel not alone this weekend I will gladley take her out for you maybe even get some slime on her.
